    • getExceptionsCaughtDuringExecution

      List<Exception> getExceptionsCaughtDuringExecution()
      Returns exceptions that were caught and collected during the execution of this plan (if any). If no exceptions were caught (which should be the normal case), then this function returns an empty list.
